=Sudimage Redirections=

This is a package for the CMS '''Concrete5'''.
Its purpose is to allow you to redirect automatically from a parent page to its first child page.

==Usage==

After installing the package, you will have a new page attribute available called ''Redirect this page to its first child page''.
When enabled and checked, the package will redirect the visitor to the page beneath itself.

==Localisation==

The package is delivered with a French language .po and .mo file.
More languages are welcome.

